{"tid":1778474,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"想捐錢、想捐物資，要點做？","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:00:06.000Z","uid":99762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd5f129cd85c44349dcc488c57afe8ccff74e0d","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"想捐錢、想捐物資，要點做？<br />\n<br />\n一，請裝 telegram<br />\n<a href=\"http://係t.me/hkstudentsneeds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BF%82t.me%2Fhkstudentsneeds&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=08be2dad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">係t.me/hkstudentsneeds</a> 入面，<br />\n自己揀想 support 邊方面<br />\n<br />\n如果唔識用/唔想用 telegram<br />\n可以捐比 612 星火<br />\n或者有活動時，自己將物資、飯卷攞去物資站<br />\n<br />\n二，諗清楚自己想捐咩及捐幾多<br />\n(大多需要面交)<br />\n以下係一啲個人推薦<br />\n<br />\n奇蹟 online<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/helpthefightguys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhelpthefightguys&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=ffca19ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/helpthefightguys</a><br />\n收物資、飯卷俾前綫<br />\n想捐比前綫，可以揀呢個<br />\n<br />\n香港魔法研究學院<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkmagicresearchschool\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmagicresearchschool&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=5a9fbe64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkmagicresearchschool</a><br />\n呢排籌錢俾去台旅行的人<br />\n極少不需面交的 channel<br />\n收 bitcoin(方法好似唔算難)<br />\n如果想避免面交，可以揀呢個<br />\n<br />\nPEE倉助養計劃<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/buyppe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbuyppe&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4662e750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/buyppe</a><br />\n人手比較充足<br />\n<br />\n前綫肉成計劃<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freedomofsummer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreedomofsummer&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=b550a084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/freedomofsummer</a><br />\nfocus 餐卷<br />\n長期資助前綫食飯<br />\n<br />\n仔女有温飽<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/FeelHongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFeelHongKong&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=348cbfb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/FeelHongKong</a><br />\n生活費<br />\n會有審查，確保一定係義士受惠<br />\n<br />\n香港人嘅物資站<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkmudg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmudg&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=c16b5255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkmudg</a><br />\n單純提供平台，買賣雙方自行面交<br />\n適宜一啲安全物品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三，捐錢、捐物資唔係贖罪卷<br />\n既然捐咗，何不走多幾步呢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n最近，有物資 channel 需要停止運作<br />\n希望大家交收都小心安全<br />\n<br />\n同埋各位唔好亂 post 野<br />\n食飯之類冇所謂<br />\n但係幫人去旅行/自己去旅行請靜靜雞<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以嘅話，share 去 fb ig<br />\n叫啲人多啲支持細 channel<br />\n好多 channel 、搞手都值得支持"},{"pid":"cef34b449dce3409dc51a026bc9a133c700f1e64","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"重開"},{"pid":"00172ddfe09003bd70e2e69aa66ba84eadb8bef2","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0bf07dde58ec26cd8981d3c82af057075538f9d","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"690e3894ac8c15940836681d93a8e06511005fa0","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70a86aadab44a8f9ceafb442a3ba82d9548341d1","tid":1778474,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"push"}]}